    <briefdescription>
<para>Template class for type-safe table metadata changes using builder pattern. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdateTyped" kindref="compound">PendingUpdateTyped</ref> extends <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdate" kindref="compound">PendingUpdate</ref> with a type-safe <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdateTyped_1afbee40c70e2b878b49a2794388ce8290" kindref="member">Apply()</ref> method that returns the specific result type for each operation. Subclasses implement specific types of table updates such as schema changes, property updates, or snapshot-producing operations like appends and deletes.</para>
<para><ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdateTyped_1afbee40c70e2b878b49a2794388ce8290" kindref="member">Apply()</ref> can be used to validate and inspect the uncommitted changes before committing. <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdate_1a0643491619bb8e88a60943e5546adcb6" kindref="member">Commit()</ref> applies the changes and commits them to the table.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>T</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The type of result returned by <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1PendingUpdateTyped_1afbee40c70e2b878b49a2794388ce8290" kindref="member">Apply()</ref> </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
